Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:53.11,OPC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you 也能相通
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.11,0:02:55.82,OPC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you 无论多么遥远
